// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0009 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 528c4440-a55a-5573-b195-d6853e7048da

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*")
